Finally, stop only when both required `submit` calls have succeeded (or dry-run Part 1 example verification is complete). Summarize results.

## Rules

- **Never** call `submit` until the puzzle example for that part passes.
- AoC rate-limits submissions to ~1/minute — if submit says rate limited, wait and retry.
- Part 2 text is **not** available until Part 1 is accepted on adventofcode.com (except finale days).
- Prefer optimizing a slow algorithm over running the full input locally.
